## Phase 5: Polish & SEO

- Responsive audit trên mọi breakpoint
- `react-helmet` cho từng trang: title, meta description, canonical, Open Graph  
- Lazy loading images, code splitting đã có sẵn qua `Loadable`
- Accessibility audit (contrast, alt text, keyboard nav)
- Performance: bundle analyze, tree shaking

---

